Documentation.Data: Název role, podle které bude autorizován uživatel. Názvy rolí jsou nastaveny dodavatelem systému a není možné je měnit.
Systémová role. Přiřazením této role uživateli bude tento uživatel autorizován k použití určitých funkcí systému. Seznam a popis rolí obdržíte od dodavatele systému.

CREATE TABLE Tmp_AsapRole ( RecordCreatedBy uniqueidentifier NULL, RecordUpdatedBy uniqueidentifier NULL, Id uniqueidentifier NOT NULL, RecordCreated datetime NULL, RecordUpdated datetime NULL, Name nvarchar(255) NOT NULL ) ON [PRIMARY]
IF EXISTS(SELECT * FROM AsapRole) EXEC('INSERT INTO Tmp_AsapRole (RecordCreatedBy, RecordUpdatedBy, Id, RecordCreated, RecordUpdated, Name) SELECT RecordCreatedBy, RecordUpdatedBy, Id, RecordCreated, RecordUpdated, Name FROM AsapRole TABLOCKX')
ALTER TABLE BusinessPartnerAsapRole DROP CONSTRAINT FK_BusinessPartnerAsapRole_refAsapRoleId_AsapRole

SchemaItem.Name: AddUser_CreateBusinessPartner
SchemaItem.M01:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <xsl:stylesheet xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" version="1.0" xmlns:AS="http://schema.advantages.cz/AsapFunctions" xmlns:date="http://exslt.org/dates-and-times" exclude-result-prefixes="AS date">
<xsl:param name="UserRoleId"/> <xsl:param name="FirstName"/> <xsl:param name="Name"/> <xsl:param name="UserName"/>
<xsl:template match="ROOT"> <ROOT> <BusinessPartner> <Id><xsl:value-of select="AS:GenerateId()"/></Id> <FirstName><xsl:value-of select="$FirstName"/></FirstName> <Name><xsl:value-of select="$Name"/></Name> <UserName><xsl:value-of select="$UserName"/></UserName>
<BusinessPartnerAsapRole Id="{AS:GenerateId()}" refAsapRoleId="{$UserRoleId}"/>
<Resource> <xsl:if test="AS:GetConstant('Authorization_NewUser_DefaultOrganizationId') != AS:GetConstant('_guid_empty')"> <xsl:attribute name="refOrganizationId"><xsl:value-of select="AS:GetConstant('Authorization_NewUser_DefaultOrganizationId')"/></xsl:attribute> </xsl:if> <Id><xsl:value-of select="AS:GenerateId()"/></Id> <Name><xsl:value-of select="concat($FirstName, ' ', $Name)"/></Name> <xsl:if test="AS:GetConstant('Authorization_NewUser_DefaultBusinessUnitId') != AS:GetConstant('_guid_empty')"> <refBusinessUnitId><xsl:value-of select="AS:GetConstant('Authorization_NewUser_DefaultBusinessUnitId')"/></refBusinessUnitId> </xsl:if> <refResourceTypeId><xsl:value-of select="AS:GetConstant('ResourceType_Human')"/></refResourceTypeId> </Resource> </BusinessPartner> </ROOT> </xsl:template> </xsl:stylesheet>
